Key Match Events: Albert Gronbaek scored his first international goal after a one-two exchange with Yussuf Poulsen.
Yussuf Poulsen scored an exquisite bicycle kick goal from Victor Kristiansen’s pinpoint cross.
Denmark achieved their 13th straight undefeated game on home soil.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Denmark's victory marks their fourth win in five head-to-heads against Serbia.
Denmark is now atop Group A4, five points above European champions Spain after two match days.
